She will be sampling three
different items today

00:02:41.240 --> 00:02:43.190
that she'll speak
to, but I wanted

00:02:43.190 --> 00:02:45.320
to please have everyone
give her a warm applause

00:02:45.320 --> 00:02:47.000
so that she can
dive into cooking.

00:02:47.000 --> 00:02:48.426
So please welcome Laura.

